{
  "title": "VimFu — The ~ Key",
  "description": "Tilde toggles the case of the character under the cursor and moves right. Uppercase to lowercase and back.",
  "speed": 0.55,
  "rows": 20,
  "cols": 40,
  "humanize": 0.7,
  "seed": 334,
  "ttsVoice": "echo",
  "playlist": "VimFu",
  "tags": [
    "vim",
    "neovim",
    "nvim",
    "vimfu",
    "tutorial",
    "terminal",
    "editor",
    "coding",
    "programming",
    "keyboard"
  ],
  "setup": [
    {
      "comment": "Set TERM for proper color support in Neovim"
    },
    {
      "line": "export TERM=xterm-256color"
    },
    {
      "comment": "Prepare workspace"
    },
    {
      "line": "mkdir -p ~/vimfu && cd ~/vimfu"
    },
    {
      "line": "rm -f hero.py .hero.py.swp .hero.py.swo"
    },
    {
      "line": "rm -f ~/.local/state/nvim/swap/*hero.py*"
    },
    {
      "comment": "Create demo file"
    },
    {
      "writeFile": "hero.py",
      "content": "name = \"link\"\nboss = \"GANON\"\nworld = \"hYrUlE\""
    },
    {
      "line": "clear"
    },
    {
      "comment": "Launch nvim before recording"
    },
    {
      "line": "nvim hero.py"
    },
    {
      "waitForScreen": "All",
      "timeout": 30.0
    },
    {
      "ifScreen": "swap file",
      "thenKeys": "d"
    }
  ],
  "steps": [
    {
      "comment": "--- Title card ---"
    },
    {
      "overlay": "VimFu",
      "caption": "The ~ Key",
      "duration": 2.0
    },
    {
      "wait": 0.7
    },
    {
      "comment": "--- Intro ---"
    },
    {
      "say": "Tilde toggles the case of the character under the cursor and advances to the next one."
    },
    {
      "wait": 0.3
    },
    {
      "comment": "--- Demo 1: capitalize first letter of link ---"
    },
    {
      "say": "The hero's name should be capitalized. Find the L. Tilde.",
      "wait": false
    },
    {
      "wait": 0.3
    },
    {
      "keys": "f\"",
      "overlay": ""
    },
    {
      "wait": 0.2
    },
    {
      "keys": "l",
      "overlay": ""
    },
    {
      "wait": 0.3
    },
    {
      "keys": "~",
      "overlay": "toggle case"
    },
    {
      "wait": 0.6
    },
    {
      "say": "Lowercase L became capital L. Link. One tilde, one character."
    },
    {
      "wait": 0.3
    },
    {
      "comment": "--- Demo 2: lowercase GANON with 5~ ---"
    },
    {
      "say": "The boss name is stuck in caps. Move down, find the G. Five tilde.",
      "wait": false
    },
    {
      "wait": 0.3
    },
    {
      "keys": "j0",
      "overlay": ""
    },
    {
      "wait": 0.2
    },
    {
      "keys": "f\"",
      "overlay": ""
    },
    {
      "wait": 0.2
    },
    {
      "keys": "l",
      "overlay": ""
    },
    {
      "wait": 0.3
    },
    {
      "keys": "5~",
      "overlay": "toggle 5 chars"
    },
    {
      "wait": 0.6
    },
    {
      "say": "GANON became ganon. Tilde takes a count, just like most Vim commands."
    },
    {
      "wait": 0.3
    },
    {
      "comment": "--- Demo 3: toggle mixed case with visual tilde ---"
    },
    {
      "say": "The world name is a mess. Mixed case everywhere. Select it and tilde.",
      "wait": false
    },
    {
      "wait": 0.3
    },
    {
      "keys": "j0",
      "overlay": ""
    },
    {
      "wait": 0.2
    },
    {
      "keys": "f\"",
      "overlay": ""
    },
    {
      "wait": 0.2
    },
    {
      "keys": "l",
      "overlay": ""
    },
    {
      "wait": 0.2
    },
    {
      "keys": "vi\"",
      "overlay": "select inner \""
    },
    {
      "wait": 0.3
    },
    {
      "keys": "~",
      "overlay": "toggle case"
    },
    {
      "wait": 0.6
    },
    {
      "say": "hYrUlE became HyRuLe. Every single character flipped. That's what toggle means."
    },
    {
      "wait": 0.3
    },
    {
      "say": "By the way, in visual mode, capital U forces uppercase and lowercase u forces lowercase. But tilde toggles."
    },
    {
      "wait": 0.3
    },
    {
      "comment": "--- Wrap up ---"
    },
    {
      "say": "Tilde. Toggle case one character at a time, with a count, or on a visual selection."
    },
    {
      "wait": 1.5
    }
  ],
  "teardown": [
    {
      "comment": "Quit nvim without saving"
    },
    "escape",
    {
      "type": ":q!"
    },
    "enter",
    {
      "comment": "Clean up"
    },
    {
      "line": "rm -f hero.py"
    }
  ],
